2026-05-16T20:31:05.8311770Z 13    <!--
2026-05-16T20:31:05.8312353Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T20:31:05.8313243Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
