2026-05-16T20:31:05.9202720Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T20:31:05.9203621Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T20:31:05.9204710Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T20:31:05.9205572Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
